# Copy to `.env.local` (gitignored) to override the API origin for `npm run dev` / `npm run build`.
# Vite only exposes variables prefixed with VITE_.
#
# Default dev setup uses `.env.development`: `VITE_API_BASE_URL=/api` (proxied by Vite → http://127.0.0.1:8000).
#
# Example when something else already uses port 8000 — run GraphClerk API on 8010 and point the UI there:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8010
